cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about weakly-supervised semantic image segmentation, which is a topic in computer vision (CV). Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a new loss function for training deep convolutional neural networks, which is a topic in machine learning (LG and NE) and artificial intelligence (AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates its method on the PASCAL VOC 2012 dataset, which is a benchmark dataset for multimedia (MM) research.
